LIST OF COMMANDS

import odgi

g = odgi.graph()  
Define graph

g.load("file")  
Load file in graph

<g>.append_step(options)
Append a visit to a node to the given path. Returns a handle to the new final step on the path which is appended.

-odgi.graph - default
-g.path_handle
-g.handle - look handle
   
